- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes an algorithm for solving optimization problems, which is a common application of AI. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses the efficiency of the proposed algorithm compared to other methods, which is a common topic in algorithm analysis. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses practical applications of the proposed algorithm in solving nonlinear, multimodal case studies.
